{
  "stem": "150.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And throughout the day, they would bring in pieces of paper showing how many they had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when it was 10,000, that was it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was already late afternoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the people on the left were told to go home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The 10,000 were taken to the Ninth Fort and executed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And here's a peculiar thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When-- I got a book at home-- you might have it also-- called the And in the back, it has statistics, and one of the statistics is the so-called Jordan List.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Jordan List is the list of how many people were executed at the Ninth Fort at any given day, and I naturally looked up October 29, 1942.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a very peculiar thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was something like 3,000 something or other Jewish men, and 4,000 something or other Jewish women, and 3,000 something or other Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by the way, it is marked, 'Elimination of superfluous Jews from Ghetto Kaunas.' And the total of all these weird numbers comes out to 9,800, 9,800.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I looked at it, and I couldn't figure it out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And 200 people stayed alive that day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe me, another one of the-- I don't know if he was drunk, or just ignorant, or maybe compassionate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is one of those strange things that happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just wanted to say something about heroism, you know, dealing with, with this strange American idea that suffering is heroism and that all survivors are heroes just because they suffered.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I think that's a bunch of hooey.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Heroism is not suffering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Heroism is doing something that you don't have to do, running into a building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Suffering deserves sympathy and tender loving care.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
